# Repo root is the build context for backend/Dockerfile and
# frontend/Dockerfile (see compose.yml) -- without these exclusions every
# image build ships ~270 MB of dependencies and git history to the daemon,
# which is slow at best and flaky at worst. Nothing here is COPY'd by any
# Dockerfile: images install their own deps (uv sync / npm ci).
.git
**/node_modules
backend/.venv
**/.venv
backend/htmlcov
frontend/dist
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
